'''乔安娜·克莱尔·叶茨'''（{{lang-en|Joanna Clare Yeates}}，1985年4月19日－2010年12月17日）是英格兰[[汉普郡|汉普郡]]景观设计师，2010年12月17日晚，她在[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]和同事一起外出后[[失踪者|失踪]]。她的亲属和警方公开呼吁广大市民提供线索，叶茨的尸体于12月25日在[[萨默塞特郡|萨默塞特郡]]北部的鄉郊小鎮[[法兰德|法兰德]]（Failand）被一对情侣发现，经[[验尸|验尸]]确认她是被人勒死。

案件调查过程代号“辮子行动”，是布里斯托尔地区历史上最大规模的警方调查之一。叶茨的家人通过[[社交网络服务|社交网络服务]]和新闻发布会请求公众协助，有关案件的报道基本主宰了这年圣诞期间的英国媒体。媒体共计提供6万英鎊悬赏金，奖励提供线索促使案犯被捕并定罪的市民。警方起初将叶茨的房东、住在同一幢楼内的克里斯托弗·杰弗里斯列为嫌疑人并将他逮捕，但之后没有提出起诉直接释放。

2011年1月20日，叶茨的邻居、32岁的[[荷兰人|荷兰裔]]工程师文森特·塔巴克被捕。这时媒体的关注焦点是[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]重现叶茨失踪过程的电视节目《[[犯罪观察|犯罪观察]]》。经过两天的盤問，检察官于2011年1月22日起诉塔巴克谋杀叶茨。2011年5月5日，塔巴克承认[[误杀|误杀]]叶茨，但并没有[[预谋杀人|预谋杀人]]。案件庭审于2011年10月4日启动，法庭于同月28日判处被告谋杀罪名成立并处以[[无期徒刑|终身监禁]]，至少20年不得[[假释|假释]]。

多家英国报纸因在案情报道过程中的不当行径遭到起诉。杰弗里斯起诉8家出版社在报道他被捕的消息时有[[诽谤|诽谤]]行为，法院支持他的起诉要求，判决报纸对他受到的实质性损害给予赔偿。《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》和《[[太阳报_(英国)|太阳报]]》因在报道中包含可能危及庭审公正性的信息而被判[[藐视法庭|藐视法庭]]罪名成立。叶茨的追悼会在她生前居住的布里斯托尔郊区的教区教堂举行，葬礼则是在她父母位于汉普郡的家附近举行。当地还计划建设多个纪念场馆，其中一个位于布里斯托尔某家新医院的花园内，这个花园正是叶茨生前为该医院设计。

== 人物背景及失踪经过 ==
乔安娜·克莱尔·叶茨于1985年4月19日在英格兰[[汉普郡|汉普郡]]出生，她的父亲叫大卫·叶茨（{{lang|en|David Yeates}}），母亲叫特雷莎·叶茨（{{lang|en|Teresa Yeates}}）<ref name="BristolPost-20111029-beautiful">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325234938/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Joanna-Yeates-beautiful-talented-young-lady/story-13697084-detail/story.html | title = Joanna Yeates was a beautiful, talented young lady destined to fly high | newspaper = Bristol Evening Post | publisher = Northcliffe Newspapers Group | date = 2011-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-04 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Joanna-Yeates-beautiful-talented-young-lady/story-13697084-detail/story.html | archivedate = 2014-03-25 }}</ref>。乔安娜在[[罗姆西|罗姆西]]附近的[[爱伯利园|爱伯利园]]（{{lang|en|Embley Park}}）接受[[私立学校|私立教育]]，再在[[彼得·西蒙兹学院|彼得·西蒙兹学院]]（{{lang|en|Peter Symonds College}}）取得[[普通教育高级程度证书|普通教育高级程度证书]]，然后又在[[瑞特尔学院|瑞特尔学院]]取得[[景观设计|景观设计]]学位<ref name="BristolPost-20111029-beautiful" /><ref name=Post-2010-12-23>{{cite news |title=Distraught parents fear the worst over missing 25-year-old Bristol woman Joanna Yeates |publisher=Northcliffe Newspapers Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903060554/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Distraught-Parents-fear-worst-missing-Bristol-25-year-old-woman/story-11297296-detail/story.html |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2010-12-23 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Distraught-Parents-fear-worst-missing-Bristol-25-year-old-woman/story-11297296-detail/story.html |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archivedate=2014-09-03 }}</ref>。接下来她进入[[格罗斯特郡大学|格罗斯特郡大学]]深造，并取得景观设计专业[[深造文凭|深造文凭]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Murdered University of Gloucestershire graduate Jo Yeates was laid to rest in the village where she grew up yesterday |newspaper=The Citizen |publisher=Northcliffe Newspaper Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325220830/http://www.gloucestercitizen.co.uk/University-Gloucestershire-graduate-Jo-Yeates-buried/story-11896529-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-03-25 |date=2011-02-12 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |url=http://www.gloucestercitizen.co.uk/University-Gloucestershire-graduate-Jo-Yeates-buried/story-11896529-detail/story.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2008年12月，叶茨在[[温彻斯特|温彻斯特]]的海兰·埃德加公司结识25岁的景观设计师格雷格·里尔登（{{lang|en|Greg Reardon}}）<ref name="BristolPost-20111029-beautiful" /><ref name="Guardian-20101225-facebook">{{cite news | last = McKie | first = Robin | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/25/joanna-yeates-disappearance-facebook | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906065047/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/25/joanna-yeates-disappearance-facebook | title = Joanna Yeates disappearance generates massive hunt on Facebook | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2010-12-25 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2014-09-06 }}</ref>，两人于2009年同居<ref>{{cite web | url = http://fandaily.info/slider/greg-reardon-is-joanna-yeates-boyfriend/ | author = Miva | work = Fandaily.info | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140302024540/http://fandaily.info/slider/greg-reardon-is-joanna-yeates-boyfriend/ | archivedate = 2014-03-02 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Greg Reardon is Joanna Yeates Boyfriend }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/dec/14/joanna-yeates-boyfriend-talks-sun | title = Joanna Yeates's boyfriend talks publicly for the first time | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | first = Steven | last = Morris | date = 2011-12-14 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151021183851/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/dec/14/joanna-yeates-boyfriend-talks-sun }}</ref>，并在公司迁至[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]后在该市定居<ref name="BristolPost-20111029-beautiful" />。叶茨之后跳槽到[[建筑设计合作公司|建筑设计合作公司]]驻布里斯托尔分部上班<ref name="Post-2010-12-23" />。2010年10月，叶茨和里尔登搬进该市克利夫顿郊区卡宁格路44号的一个套间<ref name=Guardian-2011-10-28>{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/28/joanna-yeates-case-vincent-tabak | title = Joanna Yeates murder: the full truth may never be known | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = [[卫报|The Guardian]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822222713/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/28/joanna-yeates-case-vincent-tabak | date = 2011-10-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2015-08-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

