2010年12月19日晚20点左右，里尔登从[[谢菲尔德|谢菲尔德]]回到家，发现叶茨不在。用[[电话|电话]][[短信|短信]]联系女友未果后，他在家里等待叶茨。过了一会儿他又试着拨打她的电话，但却发现叶茨的手机就在她外套口袋里，外套也还在家里。里尔登发现女友的包和钥匙都在家里，而且他们养的猫显然没有得到照料<ref name="Post-2011-10-18">{{cite news |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Vincent-Tabak-killed-Joanna-Yeates/story-13588955-detail/story.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906044940/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Vincent-Tabak-killed-Joanna-Yeates/story-13588955-detail/story.html |title=Vincent Tabak: How I killed Joanna Yeates |publisher=Northcliffe Newspaper Group |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2011-10-18 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archivedate=2014-09-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-landlord-held-on-suspicion-of-murder | title = Joanna Yeates murder: landlord questioned | work = Channel 4 News | publisher = Channel 4 | date = 2010-12-30 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324155209/http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-landlord-held-on-suspicion-of-murder | archivedate = 2014-03-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Tabak 'Strangled Joanna For 20 Seconds' | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | date = 2012-10-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111220032900/http://news.sky.com/home/uk-news/article/16090480 | accessdate = 2011-12-20 | url = http://news.sky.com/home/uk-news/article/16090480 | archivedate = 2011-12-20 }}</ref>。等到午夜还没有消息后，里尔登向警方报告叶茨失踪，并告知她的双亲<ref name="Post-2011-10-18" />。

经刑侦人员确认，叶茨曾于2010年12月17日晚和同事一起在[[公园街_(布里斯托尔)|公园街]]（{{lang|en|Park Street}}）的布里斯托尔拉姆酒吧（{{lang|en|Bristol Ram pub}}），然后在当晚20点左右离开，这里距她家步行只需30分钟<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/uk-news/joanna-yeates-murder-man-32-1859384 |title=Joanna Yeates murder: man, 32, arrested |publisher=Trinity Mirror |newspaper=Western Mail |date=2011-01-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214190843/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/uk-news/joanna-yeates-murder-man-32-1859384 |archivedate=2014-12-14 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-12-05 }}</ref><ref name="Sky-20101225">{{cite news |last=Collier |title=Prayers For Missing Jo As Search Continues |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101228223301/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Police-Continue-Search-For-Missing-Architect-As-Prayers-Said-At-Midnight-Mass/Article/201012415870484 |work=Sky News Online |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Police-Continue-Search-For-Missing-Architect-As-Prayers-Said-At-Midnight-Mass/Article/201012415870484 |date=2010-12-25 |accessdate=2010-12-28 |first=Ian |archivedate=2010-12-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。她告诉朋友和同事，这将是她搬进新家后度过的第一个没有里尔登陪伴的周末，对此她一点也不期待，打算在此期间做一些烧烤，为两人计划下周举办的聚会做准备，还打算去购物准备过圣诞节<ref name="Post-2010-12-23" /><ref name="Standard-2011-10-23">{{cite news |title=Joanna Yeates 'was dreading weekend alone in flat' |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140902115306/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/joanna-yeates-was-dreading-weekend-alone-in-flat-6453294.html |deadurl=no |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/joanna-yeates-was-dreading-weekend-alone-in-flat-6453294.html |archivedate=2014-09-02 }}</ref>。经[[闭路电视|闭路电视]]监控显示，叶茨于当晚20点10分左右离开一家[[维特罗斯|维特罗斯]]超市，但并没有买任何东西<ref name="Post-2010-12-23" /><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-12-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220145129/http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Joanna-Parents-tearful-goodbye/story-11347858-detail/story.html |url=http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Joanna-Parents-tearful-goodbye/story-11347858-detail/story.html |title=Joanna Yeates' parents say a tearful goodbye |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bath Chronicle |date=2010-12-28 |accessdate=2015-12-05 }}</ref>。20点30分，她打电话给最好的朋友丽贝卡·斯科特（{{lang|en|Rebecca Scott}}），希望在圣诞夜见面<ref name="BristolPost-20101229-help">{{cite news | publisher = Northcliffe Newspapers Group | date = 2010-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325015412/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Help-Bristol-police-killer-strangled-Clifton-architect-Joanna-Yeates/story-11290042-detail/story.html | newspaper = Bristol Evening Post | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | url = http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Help-Bristol-police-killer-strangled-Clifton-architect-Joanna-Yeates/story-11290042-detail/story.html | title = Help Bristol police find killer who strangled Clifton architect Joanna Yeates | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。另据录像显示，叶茨还于20点40分左右在一家[[乐购|乐购]]分店购买披萨饼，这也是警方找到有关她行踪的最后纪录<ref name="Sky-20101224-pictures">{{cite news |last=Norman |first=Pete |last2=Borland |first2=Huw |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-New-CCTV-Pictures-Of-Architect-Who-Disappeared-A-Week-Ago-In-Bristol/Article/201012415868004 |title=New CCTV Pictures Of Missing Architect |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227084703/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-New-CCTV-Pictures-Of-Architect-Who-Disappeared-A-Week-Ago-In-Bristol/Article/201012415868004 |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |work=Sky News Online |date=2010-10-24 |accessdate=2010-12-27 |archivedate=2010-12-27 }}</ref>。此外，她还在乐购分店附近的便利店买了两小瓶苹果酒<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://news.sky.com/story/826796/joanna-yeates-landlord-held-over-murder | title = Joanna Yeates' Landlord Held Over Murder | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | date = 2010-12-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141214150124/http://news.sky.com/story/826796/joanna-yeates-landlord-held-over-murder | archivedate = 2014-12-14 }}</ref><ref name="BBC-2010-12-29">{{cite news | work = BBC News | title = Murdered Joanna Yeates 'seen leaving with two people' | publisher = BBC | date = 2010-12-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520172226/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12089150 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12089150 | archivedate = 2011-05-20 }}</ref>。

== 搜索、公开呼吁，找到尸体 ==
里尔登同叶茨的朋友们一起設置一個网站并希望利用[[社交网络|社交网络]]尋找她的下落<ref name="Guardian-20101225-facebook" />。2010年12月21日，叶茨的父母和里尔登在警方新闻发布会现场公开呼吁，请求广大市民伸出援手，确保她平安归来<ref>{{cite news | title = Tearful parents plead: Help find our daughter | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110127234633/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/8218181/Tearful-parents-plead-Help-find-our-daughter.html | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-12-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/8218181/Tearful-parents-plead-Help-find-our-daughter.html | archivedate = 2011-01-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12050514 | title = Bristol woman's disappearance 'out of character' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520172207/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12050514 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-05-20 }}</ref>。2010年12月23日，叶茨的父亲大卫在经[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]和[[英国广播公司新闻|英国广播公司新闻]]直播的另一场新闻发布会上称：“我估计她是在回到家后再被绑架的……从留下的东西看，我完全不明白这次绑架到底是在什么情况下发生的……我只能肯定，她不会把这些东西都留在家里自己走出去，她肯定是被带到了什么地方<ref name="BBC-20101223-appeal">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12068905 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004103240/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12068905 | title = Parents of Joanna Yeates make emotional appeal | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-23 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-04 }}</ref>。”叶茨的钥匙、手机、钱包和外套都留在家里<ref name="BBC-20101227-visit">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520172221/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12081834 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12081834 | title = Joanna Yeates' family visit scene of body find | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-27 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2011-05-20 }}</ref>，警方还找到她购买披萨饼的[[收据|收据]]，但买的饼及其[[包装|包装]]都不在<ref name="Independent-20101229-captive">{{cite news | last = Hughes | first = Mark | date = 2010-12-29 | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/joanna-yeates-may-have-been-held-captive-before-her-murder-2171124.html | title = Joanna Yeates may have been held captive before her murder | newspaper = The Independent | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324155548/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/joanna-yeates-may-have-been-held-captive-before-her-murder-2171124.html | publisher = Independent Print Limited | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-24 }}</ref>。叶茨买的两小瓶苹果酒都在家里，其中一瓶已经用掉部分<ref name="BBC-2010-12-29" />。由于现场没有任何强行进入或打斗的迹象<ref name="BBC-20101227-visit" />，警方怀疑叶茨可能认识绑架她的人<ref name="Independent-20101229-captive" />。

