2010年12月25日，法兰德（{{lang|en|Failand}}）的一对情侣在朗伍德巷（{{lang|en|Longwood Lane}}）某[[高尔夫球场|高尔夫球场]]旁遛狗时发现一具衣着完好的尸体，旁边是一家[[沙石场|沙石场]]的入口，这里距叶茨的家约有4.8公里<ref name="BristolPost-20101229-help"/><ref name="BBC-20101225-found">{{cite news | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-25 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12079050 | title = Body of woman found in hunt for Joanna Yeates | publisher = BBC | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150808214657/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12079050 | archivedate = 2015-08-08 }}</ref>。经警方确认，死者就是叶茨<ref name="BBC-20101226-satisfied">{{cite news | last = Maguire | first = John | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12080254 | title = Police 'satisfied' body is missing woman Joanna Yeates | publisher = BBC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130929110935/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12080254 | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-26 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2013-09-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2010年12月27日，里尔登和叶茨的家人来到找到尸体的地点<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Family-s-visit-scene-body/story-11302724-detail/story.html |title=Joanna Yeates' family's first visit to Bristol scene where body was found |publisher=Northcliffe Newspapers Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611095305/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Family-s-visit-scene-body/story-11302724-detail/story.html |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2010-12-28 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2015-06-11 }}</ref>，大卫表示他人已经告诉过自己和家人要“做好面对最坏情况的准备”，他对女儿的尸体终于找到感到解脱<ref name="BBC-20101228-hopes">{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12086502 | title = Father of Joanna Yeates 'hopes police will catch killer' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150114045601/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12086502 | archivedate = 2015-01-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。受案件调查的影响，葬礼需要延期<ref name="BristolPost-20101229-help" />。[[病理学|病理学家]]纳特·凯莉醫生（{{lang|en|Dr Nat Carey}}）同意在2011年1月31日把尸体交还给叶茨的家人<ref name="SkyNews-20110131-released">{{cite news | last = Stallard | first = Katie | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324190254/http://news.sky.com/story/832998/joanna-yeates-body-released-to-her-family | archivedate = 2014-03-24 | url = http://news.sky.com/story/832998/joanna-yeates-body-released-to-her-family | title = Joanna Yeates' Body Released To Her Family | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | date = 2011-01-31 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 调查 ==
案件调查过程人称“辮子行动”（{{lang|en|Operation Braid}}），由[[雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊|雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊]]重案调查组[[总督察|总督察]]菲尔·琼斯（{{lang|en|Phil Jones}}）带队，动用的[[侦探|侦探]]和文职人员一共有80人<ref name="Guardian-20101228-known">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118021019/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/28/joanna-yeates-may-have-known-killer | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/28/joanna-yeates-may-have-known-killer | title = Joanna Yeates may have known her killer, say Bristol police | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2010-12-28 | archivedate = 2015-11-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，是该局历史上最大规模的警方行动之一<ref name="BristolPost-20110108-Glenis">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Tom | title = Was Joanna Yeates' killer behind the murder of Glenis Carruthers? | newspaper = Bristol Evening Post | publisher = Northcliffe Newspapers Group | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110416043330/http://www.thisisbristol.co.uk/news/DID-KILL-GLENIS/article-3079127-detail/article.html | url = http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/DID-KILL-GLENIS/story-11313089-detail/story.html | date = 2011-01-08 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2011-04-16 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。琼斯呼吁市民挺身而出，提供任何有助于抓获凶手的线索，特别是他人发现叶茨尸体前住在法兰德朗伍德附近的人都有可能是目击证人<ref name="Sky-20101228-hopes">{{cite news |last=Baker |first=Hazel |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105070054/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Landlord-Chris-Jefferies-Released-On-Police-Bail/Article/201101115876704 |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Landlord-Chris-Jefferies-Released-On-Police-Bail/Article/201101115876704 |title=Joanna Murder Suspect Released On Police Bail |work=Sky News Online |date=2011-01-02 |accessdate=2011-01-05 |archivedate=2011-01-05 }}</ref>。他还称，调查组正在寻找一名“浅色[[运动型多用途车|四轮驱动车]]”的司机问话<ref name="Independent-20110104-driver">{{cite news | last = Hughes | first = Mark | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219060447/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/police-seek-driver-of-4x4-in-yeates-murder-case-2175175.html | title = Police seek driver of 4x4 in Yeates murder case | newspaper = The Independent | publisher = Independent Print Limited | date = 2011-01-04 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-19 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/police-seek-driver-of-4x4-in-yeates-murder-case-2175175.html }}</ref>。据琼斯表示，警员已对“数以千计的电话应接不暇”，被这些电话“提供的破案线索和途径累得筋疲力尽<ref name="Guardian-20110101-released">{{cite news | last = Townsend | first = Mark | title = Chris Jefferies released on bail | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-01-01 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211034216/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/01/chris-jefferies-released-on-bail | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/01/chris-jefferies-released-on-bail | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。”警方核查的监控录像超过100小时，还检查了从叶茨家附近收集的共计29.3万公斤垃圾<ref name="Guardian-20110103-multiple">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | title = Joanna Yeates: Police not ruling out multiple killers | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-01-03 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/03/joanna-yeates-police-multiple-killers | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211040016/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/03/joanna-yeates-police-multiple-killers | archivedate = 2014-12-11 }}</ref>。[[灭罪热线|灭罪热线]]（{{lang|en|''Crime Stoppers''}}）悬赏1万[[英镑|英镑]]，奖励提供线索促使案犯被捕并定罪的市民<ref name="BBC-20101229-seen">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12089150 | title = Murdered Joanna Yeates 'seen leaving with two people' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520172226/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12089150 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 }}</ref>，《[[太阳报_(英国)|太阳报]]》也提供5万英镑赏金<ref>{{cite news | first = Steven | last = Morris | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/07/joanna-yeates-rewards-offered | title = Joanna Yeates: ￡60,000 in rewards offered to help catch killer | publisher = Guardian Media Group | work = The Guardian | date = 2011-01-07 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archive-date = 2022-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220102115228/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/07/joanna-yeates-rewards-offered }}</ref><ref name="Journalism-20110107-reward">{{cite news | last = McAthy | first = Rachel | url = https://www.journalism.co.uk/news/sun-offers--50000-reward-in-joanna-yeates-case/s2/a542204/ | title = Sun offers ￡50000 reward in Joanna Yeates case | publisher = Mousetrap Media | work = Journalism.co.uk | date = 2011-01-07 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archive-date = 2022-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220102115406/https://www.journalism.co.uk/news/sun-offers--50000-reward-in-joanna-yeates-case/s2/a542204/ }}</ref>。政府当局建议当地居民关好门窗，还警告女性夜间不要单独在外<ref name="Guardian-20110102-warn">{{cite news | last = Morris | title = Joanna Yeates police warn public to be watchful while killer remains at large | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150926034420/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/02/joanna-yeates-police-safety-warning | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/02/joanna-yeates-police-safety-warning | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | first = Steven | archivedate = 2015-09-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。叶茨的父亲于12月29日就案件调查接受采访时称：“我担心犯案人永远都不会投案，但我们还是期望警方能够找到此事的罪魁祸首<ref name="BristolPost-20101229-help" />。”

