发现叶茨的尸体后，雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊的探员呼吁任何掌握相关线索的市民同警方联系<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12080254 | title = Police 'satisfied' body is missing woman Joanna Yeates | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-26 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2013-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130929110935/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12080254 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Post mortem results on body of architect due to be released | newspaper = Oxford Mail | publisher = Newsquest | date = 2010-12-27 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229160219/http://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/8757749.Police_to_reveal_how_Joanna_Yeates_died/?ref=rc | url = http://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/8757749.Police_to_reveal_how_Joanna_Yeates_died/?ref=rc }}</ref>，同时还对情况类似的其它案件进行研究。这些类似案件中警方特别关注的包括：1974年被勒死的20岁女子格伦尼斯·卡拉瑟斯（{{lang|en|Glenis Carruthers}}）；1996年失踪的25岁女性[[梅兰妮·霍尔谋杀案|梅兰妮·霍尔]]（{{lang|en|Melanie Hall}}），她的尸体直到13年后才寻获；此外还有2009年失踪的35岁妇女[[克劳迪娅·劳伦斯失踪案|克劳迪娅·劳伦斯]]（{{lang|en|Claudia Lawrence}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article2855391.ece |title=Killing similar to death of Melanie Hall 14 years ago |publisher=Times Newspapers Ltd |newspaper=The Times |date=2010-12-27 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140325170558/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article2855391.ece |subscription=yes |archivedate=2014-03-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="DailyTelegraph-20101226">{{cite news | last = Leach | first = Ben | last2 = Howie | first2 = Michael | last3 = Harrison | first3 = David | title = Parents of missing architect Joanna Yeates: 'we knew she had been abducted' | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2010-12-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229161713/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/majornews/8225193/Parents-of-missing-architect-Joanna-Yeates-we-knew-she-had-been-abducted.html | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/majornews/8225193/Parents-of-missing-architect-Joanna-Yeates-we-knew-she-had-been-abducted.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Savage | first = Michael | title = Police try to unlock riddle of landscape architect's final hours | publisher = Independent Print Limited | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2010-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229182355/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/police-try-to-unlock-riddle-of-landscape-architects-final-hours-2169851.html | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/police-try-to-unlock-riddle-of-landscape-architects-final-hours-2169851.html }}</ref><ref name="DailyTelegraph-20101231-1974-killing">{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | last = Savill | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229161816/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8234674/Joanna-Yeates-murder-neighbour-interviewed-by-police-over-boyfriends-flat-battery-incident.html | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | first = Richard | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8234674/Joanna-Yeates-murder-neighbour-interviewed-by-police-over-boyfriends-flat-battery-incident.html | title = Joanna Yeates murder: police review unsolved 1974 killing | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2010-12-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。调查人员认定，叶茨案和霍尔案存在“惊人的类似之处”，两人年龄和外表接近，而且都是见过朋友并回家后再失踪<ref>{{cite news | last = Savill | first = Richard | title = Joanna Yeates: parents lay flowers near where body was found | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-12-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229164913/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8227329/Joanna-Yeates-parents-lay-flowers-near-where-body-was-found.html | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8227329/Joanna-Yeates-parents-lay-flowers-near-where-body-was-found.html }}</ref>，不过警方之后没有特别针对这些联系进行大张旗鼓的调查<ref name="Guardian-20110101-released" />。警方取得[[克利夫顿吊桥|克利夫顿吊桥]]的监控录像，因为如果要从叶茨最后一次被他人看到的克利夫顿（{{lang|en|Clifton}}）到达发现尸体的地方，这里是最直接的路线<ref name="DailyTelegraph-20110112-avoided" /><ref name="Sky-2010-12-28" />。但是，监控录像的清晰度很差，根本不可能看清车上的人或是车牌号码<ref>{{cite news | last = Pilditch | first = David | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20141229165005/http://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/222191/Poor-CCTV-film-may-let-Joanna-Yeates-killer-escape | url = http://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/222191/Poor-CCTV-film-may-let-Joanna-Yeates-killer-escape | title = Poor CCTV film may let Joanna Yeates killer escape | newspaper = Daily Express | publisher = Express Group Newspapers | date = 2011-01-10 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。警方还得知，凶手有可能向南多走不到一英里，通过[[雅芳河_(布里斯托)|雅芳河]]上的雅芳大桥来避开监控<ref name="DailyTelegraph-20110112-avoided" />。

[[验尸|验尸]]工作从2010年12月26日开始，但尸体的冻结程度导致给出结果的时间相应延迟<ref name="ITN-20101227-delay">{{cite news | url = http://news.uk.msn.com/articles.aspx?cp-documentid=155692336 | title = Police delay Joanna Yeates' post mortem results | publisher = MSN | work = MSN News | date = 2010-12-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325193056/http://news.uk.msn.com/articles.aspx?cp-documentid=155692336 | accessdate = 2014-03-25 | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。警方起初认为，叶茨有可能是冻死的，因为她身上并没有任何可见的伤痕<ref>{{cite news |title=Police are understood to be investigating the possibility Joanna Yeates may have frozen to death on the lonely country lane where she was found. |publisher=Local World |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220145129/http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Joanna-Parents-tearful-goodbye/story-11347858-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-12-20 |newspaper=Bath Chronicle |date=2010-12-28 |accessdate=2015-12-06 |url=http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Joanna-Parents-tearful-goodbye/story-11347858-detail/story.html }}</ref>。2010年12月28日，警方宣布病理学家经验尸确定叶茨是被勒死的，所以案件正式归类为谋杀<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Joanna+'was+strangled'+MURDER+HUNT+IS+LAUNCHED+OVER+DEATH+OF...-a0245366135 |title=Joanna 'was strangled' Murder hunt is launched over death of 25-year-old |newspaper=Liverpool Daily Post |publisher=Trinity Mirror |date=2010-12-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140905173754/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Joanna+'was+strangled'+MURDER+HUNT+IS+LAUNCHED+OVER+DEATH+OF...-a0245366135 |accessdate=2015-12-06 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-09-05 }}</ref>。验尸结果表明，受害人应该是在尸体于圣诞节被人发现前几天就已死亡<ref name="BBC-20101228-strangled">{{cite news | last = Maguire | first = John | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520172223/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12084756 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12084756 | title = Bristol architect Joanna Yeates was strangled, say police | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 }}</ref>，同时叶茨体内也没有她之前购买的披萨饼<ref name="SkyNews-20110119-contact">{{cite news |last=Brunt |first=Martin |last2=Arnold |first2=Adam |title=Joanna Yeates Murder: 300 People Contact Cops |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |work=Sky News Online |date=2011-01-19 |accessdate=2011-01-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110123223928/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Police-Receive-Over-300-Phone-Calls-And-Emails-In-24-Hour-Period/Article/201101315899469 |archivedate=2011-01-23 |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Police-Receive-Over-300-Phone-Calls-And-Emails-In-24-Hour-Period/Article/201101315899469 }}</ref>。据琼斯表示，警方没有找到任何证据证明乔安娜有受到性侵犯<ref name="Independent-20110104-driver" />，此外，出于标准程序需要，警方还搜查了里尔登的笔记本电脑和手机<ref name="BBC-20101228-strangled" />，之后认定他没有犯罪嫌疑而作为证人对待<ref>{{cite news | title = Boyfriend Greg not a suspect in architect's murder, say police | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141213180040/http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Boyfriend-Greg-suspect-architect-s-murder-say-police/story-11648224-detail/story.html | publisher = Local World | newspaper = Derby Telegraph | date = 2010-12-29 | url = http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Boyfriend-Greg-suspect-architect-s-murder-say-police/story-11648224-detail/story.html | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

叶茨失踪当晚，在她家附近另一幢房子里参加聚会的某青年女子称，曾在晚上21点过后不久听到叶茨的家方向传来两声惊叫<ref>{{cite news | last = Roberts | first = Laura | title = Joanna Yeates murder: screams heard the night architect went missing | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2010-12-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8230979/Joanna-Yeates-murder-screams-heard-the-night-architect-went-missing.html | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140905213347/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8230979/Joanna-Yeates-murder-screams-heard-the-night-architect-went-missing.html }}</ref>。住在叶茨家后面的另一位邻居称他曾听到某个女人大喊“救命”，但想不起具体的时间<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906002920/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/NEIGHBOUR-HEARD-HELP/story-11245954-detail/story.html |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/NEIGHBOUR-HEARD-HELP/story-11245954-detail/story.html |title=Joanna Yeates murder case: Neighbour heard cry for help |publisher=Northcliffe Newspapers Group |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2011-01-22 |accessdate=2015-12-06 |archivedate=2014-09-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。警方拆掉叶茨家的前门，希望能找到衣物纤维和{{lang|en|[[脱氧核糖核酸|DNA]]}}证据<ref name="BBC-20101229-seen" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Caroline | last = Gammell | first2 = Richard | last2 = Savill | title = Joanna Yeates 'seen leaving flat with two other people' | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2010-12-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8229426/Joanna-Yeates-seen-leaving-flat-with-two-other-people.html | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140905215908/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8229426/Joanna-Yeates-seen-leaving-flat-with-two-other-people.html }}</ref>，并核实凶手是否有可能在叶茨返回前就已潜入她家<ref name="Standard-2011-10-23"/><ref>{{cite news | title = Joanna Yeates murder: the unanswered questions | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508065721/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8236209/Joanna-Yeates-murder-the-unanswered-questions.html | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8236209/Joanna-Yeates-murder-the-unanswered-questions.html | archivedate = 2014-05-08 | date = 2011-01-02 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 }}</ref>。

=== 进一步调查 ===
调查案件的资深探员请求[[英国国家警务改善局|英国国家警务改善局]]协助，该机构会向疑难案件提供专业建议。2011年1月4日，一名曾参与多宗杀人要案调查的临床[[法庭心理学|法医心理学家]]加入调查组，希望能减少潜在嫌犯的数量<ref name="SkyNews-20110104-profiler">{{cite news |last=Brunt |first=Martin |archivedate=2011-01-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110107074456/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Inquiry-Criminal-Profiler-To-Help-Find-Killer-Of-Landscape-Architect/Article/201101115879890 |accessdate=2011-01-07 |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/UK-News/Joanna-Yeates-Murder-Inquiry-Criminal-Profiler-To-Help-Find-Killer-Of-Landscape-Architect/Article/201101115879890 |title=Exclusive: Criminal Profiler Aiding Jo Police |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |work=Sky News Online |date=2011-01-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。琼斯称手下警员已经确立上千条线索<ref name="BristolPost-20110108-Glenis" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Steven | last = Morris | first2 = Josh | last2 = Halliday | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/05/joanna-yeates-murder-missing-sock | title = Joanna Yeates detectives focus on missing sock as extra officers drafted in | publisher = Guardian Media Group | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324171218/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/05/joanna-yeates-murder-missing-sock | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-01-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2014-03-24 }}</ref>，他还说：“我可以向你保证，我们有决心破案，把杀害乔的凶手绳之于法”<ref>{{cite news |title=Jo: More than one killer? Police issue fresh appeal |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140324140256/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/JO:+MORE+THAN+ONE+KILLER%3F+Police+issue+fresh+appeal.-a0245737278 |newspaper=Middlesbrough Evening Gazette |date=2011-01-04 |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/JO%3A+MORE+THAN+ONE+KILLER%3F+Police+issue+fresh+appeal.-a0245737278 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-03-24 |accessdate=2015-12-06 }}</ref>。1月5日，琼斯透露叶茨的尸体身上少穿了一只袜子，这只袜子不在她家，也不在发现尸体的地方<ref name="BBC-20110105-missing">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150808085014/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12117460 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12117460 | title = Jo Yeates' body missing a sock when found, say police | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-01-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-06 | archivedate = 2015-08-08 }}</ref>。

警方通过{{lang|en|[[Facebook|Facebook]]}}向全国范围发起宣传活动，呼吁目击者提供线索<ref>{{cite news | last = Morrir | first = Steven | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/04/joanna-yeates-facebook-appeal | title = Joanna Yeates police launch Facebook appeal to find killer | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906020545/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/04/joanna-yeates-facebook-appeal | date = 2011-01-04 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-09-06 }}</ref>。相应页面于2011年1月4日建立，到次日已有近25万次查阅<ref>{{cite news | last = Rayner | first = Gordon | title = Joanna Yeates 'may have been strangled with own sock' | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | work = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2011-01-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140118184638/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8241098/Joanna-Yeates-may-have-been-strangled-with-own-sock.html | archivedate = 2014-01-18 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8241098/Joanna-Yeates-may-have-been-strangled-with-own-sock.html }}</ref>，有关叶茨的闭路监控画面到1月5日时在{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}上已有12万人次观看<ref name="Sky-20110105-missing">{{cite news | last = Mitchell | first = Gary | title = Murdered Joanna Yeates Had One Sock Missing | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | date = 2011-01-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906064501/http://news.sky.com/story/829237/murdered-joanna-yeates-had-one-sock-missing | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://news.sky.com/story/829237/murdered-joanna-yeates-had-one-sock-missing | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-09-06 }}</ref>。

2011年1月9日，[[英国下议院|英国下议院]][[东布里斯托尔_(英国国会选区)|东布里斯托尔]]议员[[克里·麦卡锡|克里·麦卡锡]]（{{lang|en|Kerry McCarthy}}）表态称，如果警方觉得会有帮助，她支持开展公共{{lang|en|DNA}}筛查。雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊曾于1955年对当时18岁的路易丝·史密斯（{{lang|en|Louise Smith}}）失踪一案开展大规模{{lang|en|DNA}}筛查。麦卡锡还提议，筛查范围不应局限在克利夫顿，还应当包括整个布里斯托尔地区。<ref name="BBC-20110108-MP">{{cite news | title = Jo Yeates murder case: MP backs DNA testing | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-01-09 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150808010222/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12145602 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12145602 | archivedate = 2015-08-08 }}</ref>之前從叶茨尸身上套取的{{lang|en|DNA}}已经用於检测，准备用于潜在嫌疑人的[[遗传指纹分析|比对]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Collins | first = Nick | title = Joanna Yeates murder: police could use DNA sample to trace killer | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2011-01-12 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140506074400/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8254116/Joanna-Yeates-murder-police-could-use-DNA-sample-to-trace-killer.html | archivedate = 2014-05-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8254116/Joanna-Yeates-murder-police-could-use-DNA-sample-to-trace-killer.html }}</ref><ref name="Guardian-2012-01-17">{{cite news | title = CSI Oxford: behind the scenes at Britain's top forensic lab | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | first = Jon | last = Henley | date = 2012-01-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151030174524/http://www.theguardian.com/science/2012/jan/17/csi-oxford-lgc-forensics | url = http://www.theguardian.com/science/2012/jan/17/csi-oxford-lgc-forensics | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-30 }}</ref>。警方还开始追踪生活在其管辖范围内数百个[[性罪犯登记|已登記性罪犯]]，确立他们12月17日的行踪<ref>{{cite news | first1 = Gordon | last = Rayner | first2 = Martin | last2 = Evans | first3 = Richard | last3 = Savill | title = Joanna Yeates murder: detectives to track all sex offenders in Bristol area | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2011-01-08 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906202910/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8247347/Joanna-Yeates-murder-detectives-to-track-all-sex-offenders-in-Bristol-area.html | archivedate = 2014-09-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8247347/Joanna-Yeates-murder-detectives-to-track-all-sex-offenders-in-Bristol-area.html }}</ref>。

=== 逮捕及犯罪过程重现 ===
2010年12月30日早上7点刚过，叶茨的房东、住在同一幢楼内的克里斯托弗·杰弗里斯（{{lang|en|Christopher Jefferies}}）被警方以谋杀罪名逮捕。他被带到当地警局问话，同时取证人员对他的公寓进行偵查<ref name="BBC-20101230">{{cite news | last = Geoghegan | first = Ben | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-12092509 | title = Man arrested in Joanna Yeates murder inquiry | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-30 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140511071314/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-12092509 | archivedate = 2014-05-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。12月31日，一名高级警察批准调查人员将拘留时间延长12小时，以便继续向杰弗里斯问话<ref>{{cite news | title = Joanna Yeates murder police given more time to quiz landlord | work = UTV Live News | publisher = UTV Media | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105112256/http://www.u.tv/articles/article.aspx?cat=News&guid=4e8cd5a4-54cc-4110-bc92-84f24b625745 | url = http://www.u.tv/articles/article.aspx?cat=News&guid=4e8cd5a4-54cc-4110-bc92-84f24b625745 | date = 2010-12-31 | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-05 }}</ref><ref name="BBC-20101231-concerns">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150808153633/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12100015 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12100015 | title = Coverage of Yeates murder 'concerns' attorney general | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2010-12-31 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2015-08-08 }}</ref>。警方之后还向裁判官请求进一步延长嫌疑人的拘留时限，并分别在12月31日和2011年1月1日两度获准<ref name="Channel4-2013-12-31">{{cite news | title = Police given more time to quiz Joanna Yeates murder suspect | work = Channel 4 News | publisher = Channel 4 | date = 2010-12-31 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-murder-landlord-still-being-questioned | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325190133/http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-murder-landlord-still-being-questioned | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Damian |last=Pearse |first2=Rob |last2=Cole |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325173414/http://news.sky.com/story/826851/jo-murder-further-extension-to-quiz-landlord |url=http://news.sky.com/story/826851/jo-murder-further-extension-to-quiz-landlord |title=Jo Murder: Further Extension To Quiz Landlord |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting Limited |work=Sky News Online |date=2011-01-01 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archivedate=2014-03-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。办案人员将杰弗里斯[[英格兰和威尔士的警察权力|作为嫌犯拘留了96小时]]<ref name="Channel4-2013-12-31" />，但最终还是不得不在两天后准许他保释<ref name="BBC-20110102-bailed">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12103905 | title = Landlord Chris Jefferies bailed over Jo Yeates murder | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-01-02 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140511071317/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12103905 | archivedate = 2014-05-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Denham | first = Jess | title = Joanna Yeates' 'eccentric' landlord Christopher Jefferies to be focus of new ITV drama | publisher = Independent Print Limited | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2013-11-05 | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/joanna-yeates-eccentric-landlord-christopher-jefferies-to-be-focus-of-new-itv-drama-8922063.html | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-03-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140301011251/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/joanna-yeates-eccentric-landlord-christopher-jefferies-to-be-focus-of-new-itv-drama-8922063.html }}</ref>。杰弗里斯聘请司徒高义合股律师事务所作为自己的法律代表行事<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324172938/http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Lawyers-warn-media-Jo-case-coverage/story-11340901-detail/story.html |title=The lawyers representing Christopher Jefferies say "his name has been blackened, and his privacy invaded" during the Joanna Yeates murder investigation. |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bath Chronicle |url=http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Lawyers-warn-media-Jo-case-coverage/story-11340901-detail/story.html |date=2011-01-05 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |archivedate=2014-03-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2011年3月4日，警方释放杰弗里斯并宣布他没有做案嫌疑<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-12664581 | title = Landlord Chris Jefferies is not a suspect | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-03-07 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140511071320/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-12664581 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Landlord Chris Jefferies puts Bristol flat on the market | work = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2011-03-07 | last = Hough | first = Andrew | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012073127/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/property/propertynews/8365548/Joanna-Yeates-murder-landlord-Chris-Jefferies-puts-Bristol-flat-on-the-market.html | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/property/news/8365548/Joanna-Yeates-murder-landlord-Chris-Jefferies-puts-Bristol-flat-on-the-market.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。多家媒体在杰弗里斯被捕后发表对他名誉不利的报道，对此他以[[诽谤|诽谤]]罪名起诉，从警局获释后他也在这些诉讼中获胜，但所获得的赔偿金数额不得而知<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.uk.msn.com/uk/libel-damages-for-joanna-landlord-1 | title = Libel damages for Joanna landlord | publisher = MSN | work = MSN News | date = 2011-07-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105110904/http://news.uk.msn.com/uk/libel-damages-for-joanna-landlord-1 | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警方还对调查过程可能对他造成的任何不便致歉<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-24104834 | work = BBC News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211115821/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-24104834 | title = Christopher Jefferies told 'sorry' by police over arrest distress | publisher = BBC | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-11 }}</ref>。

2011年1月，英国广播公司电视节目《犯罪观察》（{{lang|en|''Crimewatch''}}）在布里斯托尔地区取景拍摄重现案发过程的节目，并于同月26日播出<ref name="SkyNews-20110119-contact" />。曾参与[[哈利·波特系列电影|《哈利·波特》系列电影]]制作、总部位于[[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]]的[[雪花商务公司|雪花商务公司]]签约重现叶茨失踪期间布里斯托尔地区白雪皑皑的天气情况<ref>{{cite news | title = Jo Yeates murder: Crimewatch crew use Hollywood techniques for reconstruction | url = http://swns.com/news/jo-yeates-murder-crimewatch-crew-use-hollywood-techniques-for-reconstruction-13913/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141227022737/http://swns.com/news/jo-yeates-murder-crimewatch-crew-use-hollywood-techniques-for-reconstruction-13913/ | publisher = South West News Service | date = 2011-01-19 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-12-27 }}</ref>。叶茨生前最后活动的重现和拍摄于1月18日进行，媒体开始就节目进行报道后的24小时里，已经有300余人联系警方<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/30/joanna-yeates-disappearance-murder-timeline | title = Joanna Yeates timeline | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211032436/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/30/joanna-yeates-disappearance-murder-timeline | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。案情出现突破性进展，刑侦人员估计，凶手可能是使用大型[[手提袋|手提袋]]或手提箱来转移受害者的尸体<ref>{{cite news | title = Jo Yeates killer 'could have taken her from flat in suitcase' | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = Daily Telegraph | first = Andy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141227081030/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8270593/Jo-Yeates-killer-could-have-taken-her-from-flat-in-suitcase.html | last = Bloxham | date = 2011-01-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8270593/Jo-Yeates-killer-could-have-taken-her-from-flat-in-suitcase.html | archivedate = 2014-12-27 }}</ref>。

1月20日清晨，雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊逮捕32岁的[[荷兰人|荷兰裔]]工程师文森特·塔巴克（{{lang|en|Vincent Tabak}}），他和女友一起住在叶茨隔壁的公寓<ref>{{cite news | first1 = David | last1 = Harrison | first2 = Michael | last2 = Howie | first3 = Sean | last3 = Rayment | title = Jo Yeates did not know Vincent Tabak, says her father | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2011-01-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140506071346/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8276162/Jo-Yeates-did-not-know-Vincent-Tabak-says-her-father.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8276162/Jo-Yeates-did-not-know-Vincent-Tabak-says-her-father.html }}</ref><ref name="Guardian-2011-01-20">{{cite news | last1 = Morris | first1 = Steven | last2 = Walker | first2 = Peter | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211013159/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/20/joanna-yeates-police-search-neighbour-flat | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/20/joanna-yeates-police-search-neighbour-flat | title = Joanna Yeates murder: Police search neighbour's flat | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-01-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，由于之前杰弗里斯被捕期间多家媒体的报道有违相应法规并引发争议和司法诉讼，这次当局拒绝透露嫌犯受审的详细进展<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211023052/http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-murder-police-search-neighbours-flat | url = http://www.channel4.com/news/joanna-yeates-murder-police-search-neighbours-flat | title = Joanna Yeates murder: police search neighbour's flat | publisher = Channel 4 | work = Channel 4 News | date = 2011-01-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first1 = Caroline | last1 = Gammell | first2 = Nick | last2 = Britten | first3 = Richard | last3 = Savill | title = Man next door arrested over Joanna Yeates murder | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2011-01-21 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906223332/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8272836/Man-next-door-arrested-over-Joanna-Yeates-murder.html | archivedate = 2014-09-06 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8272836/Man-next-door-arrested-over-Joanna-Yeates-murder.html }}</ref>。塔巴克被捕主要是因为某女性的匿名举报，就在《犯罪观察》播出叶茨的父母请求广大市民伸出援手的节目播出后不久<ref>{{cite news | last = Harrison | first = David | title = Jo Yeates did not know Vincent Tabak, says her father | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140506071346/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8276162/Jo-Yeates-did-not-know-Vincent-Tabak-says-her-father.html | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8276162/Jo-Yeates-did-not-know-Vincent-Tabak-says-her-father.html | deadurl = no | date = 2011-01-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-05-06 }}</ref>。警方将卡宁格路暂时封闭，并在叶茨家周围搭建脚手架<ref name="Guardian-2011-01-20" />，还把塔巴克的公寓封死<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211044042/http://www.westerndailypress.co.uk/Police-search-Bath-engineer-s-flat-murder-probe/story-12340775-detail/story.html |date=2011-01-21 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |publisher=Local WSorld |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.westerndailypress.co.uk/Police-search-Bath-engineer-s-flat-murder-probe/story-12340775-detail/story.html |title=Police search Bath engineer's flat for second day in murder probe |newspaper=Western Daily Press |archivedate=2014-12-11 }}</ref><ref name="SWNS-20110120-flats">{{cite news | title = Tarpaulin put around Jo Yeates' and neighbour Vincent Tabak's flats | url = http://swns.com/news/tarpaulin-put-around-jo-yeates-and-neighbour-vincent-tabaks-flats-13962/ | last = Hearn | first = Adrian | agency = South West News Service | date = 2011-01-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150611190057/http://swns.com/news/tarpaulin-put-around-jo-yeates-and-neighbour-vincent-tabaks-flats-13962/ | archivedate = 2015-06-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。据信塔巴克被捕前曾住在某个朋友的联排别墅，距他家约1英里路径，所以刑侦人员也搜查了这里<ref name="SWNS-20110120-friend">{{cite news | last = Hearn | first = Adrian | title = Officers search flat of Vincent Tabak's friend | publisher = South West News Service | date = 2011-01-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150606122548/http://swns.com/news/officers-search-flat-of-vincent-tabaks-friend-13977/ | url = http://swns.com/news/officers-search-flat-of-vincent-tabaks-friend-13977/ | archivedate = 2015-06-06 }}</ref>。警方曾在调查初期排除塔巴克的作案嫌疑，他此前曾休假前往荷兰，探望家人后再返回英国<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211022756/http://www.channel4.com/news/yeates-murder-police-hold-neighbour-for-questioning | url = http://www.channel4.com/news/yeates-murder-police-hold-neighbour-for-questioning | title = Yeates murder: police hold neighbour for questioning | publisher = Channel 4 | work = Channel 4 News | date = 2011-01-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | script-title = en:Murdered Joanna Yeates ‘was in neighbour’s car boot as he shopped at Asda’ | publisher = Yorkshire Post Newspapers | newspaper = Yorkshire Post | date = 2011-10-10 | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211022418/http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/main-topics/general-news/murdered-joanna-yeates-was-in-neighbour-s-car-boot-as-he-shopped-at-asda-1-3857053 | url = http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/news/main-topics/general-news/murdered-joanna-yeates-was-in-neighbour-s-car-boot-as-he-shopped-at-asda-1-3857053 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Jo murder suspect quizzed for a third day | newspaper = Daily Echo | publisher = Newsquest | date = 2011-01-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211034307/http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/briefing/joanna_yeates/news/8807185.Jo_murder_suspect_quizzed_for_a_third_day/ | url = http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/briefing/joanna_yeates/news/8807185.Jo_murder_suspect_quizzed_for_a_third_day/ }}</ref>。

塔巴克被捕后，英国广播公司取消在《犯罪观察》播出重现叶茨案经过节目的原有计划<ref name="SWNS-20110125-cancelled">{{cite news | last = Hearn | first = Adrian | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325191507/http://swns.com/news/jo-yeates-crimewatch-reconstruction-cancelled-14242/ | url = http://swns.com/news/jo-yeates-crimewatch-reconstruction-cancelled-14242/ | deadurl = yes | title = Jo Yeates Crimewatch reconstruction cancelled | agency = South West News Service | date = 2011-01-25 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 }}</ref>。1月31日，多张此前未经公布过的叶茨照片通过该节目网站发布<ref>{{cite news | first = Steven | last = Morris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325164444/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/31/body-of-joanna-yeates-released | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/31/body-of-joanna-yeates-released | title = Man accused of murdering Joanna Yeates likely to face trial in October | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-01-31 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 }}</ref>。

=== {{lang|en|DNA}}检验 ===
叶茨案的{{lang|en|DNA}}检验由私营公司{{lang|en|[[LGC|LGC]]}}负责，该公司已为多起刑事案提供法医分析服务。体液和{{lang|en|DNA}}专家林赛·莱伦（{{lang|en|Lindsey Lennen}}）所在小组主要负责分析受害人身上找到的{{lang|en|DNA}}证据，据她所说，虽然{{lang|en|DNA}}检测结果指向塔巴克，但可靠性还不够。小组采用的检验方法叫“{{lang|en|DNA SenCE}}”，通过提纯和浓缩来增强原本不可用{{lang|en|DNA}}样本的可靠性：“我们无法确定这些{{lang|en|DNA}}究竟是来自唾液、精液甚至碰触，但我们可以肯定，{{lang|en|DNA}}同塔巴克不相符的可能性不足10亿分之一。”<ref name="Guardian-2012-01-17" />

== 司法诉讼和凶手 ==
[[File:Horfield_Prison,_Bristol.jpg|thumb]]

=== 谋杀指控和认罪 ===
经过审问和96小时的拘留，塔巴克于2011年1月22日被控谋杀乔安娜·叶茨。1月24日，他在布里斯托尔的[[裁判司署|裁判法院]]短暂露面，同时仍由警方收监<ref name="BBC-20110124">{{cite news | title = Jo Yeates murder accused Vincent Tabak in court | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-01-24 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120202035243/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-12262194 | archivedate = 2012-02-02 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-12262194 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。聆讯时间定在1月25日，塔巴克的律师保罗·库克（{{lang|en|Paul Cook}}）没有为当事人申请取保候审。为保障嫌犯安全，有关部门将塔巴克从[[布里斯托尔监狱|布里斯托尔监狱]]转移<ref name="SWNS-20110124-reviewing" />，暂时关押在[[伍斯特郡|伍斯特郡]][[韦查冯|韦查冯区]][[伊夫舍姆|伊夫舍姆]]（{{lang|en|Evesham}}）附近的[[朗拉丁监狱|朗拉丁监狱]]，并加以[[自杀监控|自杀监控]]<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324184250/http://www.eveshamjournal.co.uk/news/8816703.Jo_Yeates_murder_accused_on_suicide_watch_at_Long_Lartin/ | archivedate = 2014-03-24 | newspaper = Evesham Journal | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.eveshamjournal.co.uk/news/8816703.Jo_Yeates_murder_accused_on_suicide_watch_at_Long_Lartin/ | title = Jo Yeates murder accused on suicide watch at Long Lartin | date = 2011-01-27 }}</ref>。塔巴克远在荷兰的亲朋好友开始为他的法庭辩护筹资<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Bingham | first1 = John | last2 = Tweedie | first2 = Neil | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925084732/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8280005/Joanna-Yeates-murder-suspect-Vincent-Tabak-enjoyed-normal-family-Christmas.html | archivedate = 2012-09-25 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8280005/Joanna-Yeates-murder-suspect-Vincent-Tabak-enjoyed-normal-family-Christmas.html | title = Joanna Yeates murder suspect Vincent Tabak 'enjoyed normal family Christmas' | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2011-01-24 }}</ref>。

塔巴克一度声称自己与叶茨的死毫不相干，那些指控他的{{lang|en|DNA}}证据是腐败官员栽赃陷害。但到了2月8日，他又告知[[监狱宗教|监狱牧师]]彼得·布拉瑟顿（{{lang|en|Peter Brotherton}}）自己的确杀了她，打算认罪。<ref name="Telegraph-2011-10-11">{{cite news | last = Rayner | first = Gordon | title = Vincent Tabak told prison chaplain 'I killed Joanna Yeates' | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2011-10-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141205073122/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8820130/Vincent-Tabak-told-prison-chaplain-I-killed-Joanna-Yeates.html | archivedate = 2014-12-05 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8820130/Vincent-Tabak-told-prison-chaplain-I-killed-Joanna-Yeates.html }}</ref>

2011后5月5日，文森特·塔巴克承认[[英格兰法律中的误杀罪|误杀]]叶茨，但否认自己有杀人预谋<ref name="Sky050511-Manslaughter">{{cite news | title = Tabak Pleads Guilty To Killing Joanna Yeates | deadurl = no | url = http://news.sky.com/story/853999/tabak-pleads-guilty-to-killing-joanna-yeates | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | accessdate = 2011-05-08 | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610194425/http://news.sky.com/story/853999/tabak-pleads-guilty-to-killing-joanna-yeates }}</ref>，但是，[[英国皇家检控署|英国皇家检控署]]拒绝接受他的认罪<ref name="Sky050511-Manslaughter" /><ref name="Guardian050511-admits">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | title = Yeates' neighbour admits killing | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-05-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231062509/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/05/joanna-yeates-neighbour-admits-killing | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/may/05/joanna-yeates-neighbour-admits-killing | archivedate = 2013-12-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月20日，塔巴克在[[布里斯托尔皇家法院|布里斯托尔皇家法院]]参加预审聆讯，之前几次聆讯都是嫌疑人通过视频参加，一直没有离开监狱<ref name="Guardian20September2011">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231105700/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/sep/20/joanna-yeates-vincent-tabak-trial | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/sep/20/joanna-yeates-vincent-tabak-trial | title = Joanna Yeates' parents encounter killer Vincent Tabak in court | publisher = Guardian Media Group | work = The Guardian | first = Steven | last = Morris | date = 2011-09-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2013-12-31 }}</ref>。

=== 文森特·塔巴克 ===
文森特·塔巴克生于1978年2月10日，荷兰裔人士，职业是工程师<ref>{{cite news | first = Steven | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211040013/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/24/vincent-tabak-court-joanna-yeates-murder-charge | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/24/vincent-tabak-court-joanna-yeates-murder-charge | title = Vincent Tabak in court on Joanna Yeates murder charge | last = Morris | publisher = Guardian Media Group | work = The Guardian | date = 2011-01-24 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，从2007年就开始在英国居住和工作<ref name="Guardian28102011">{{cite news | title = Vincent Tabak and the porn searches the jury did not hear about | publisher = Guardian Media Group | work = The Guardian | first = Steven | last = Morris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211040013/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/24/vincent-tabak-court-joanna-yeates-murder-charge | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/jan/24/vincent-tabak-court-joanna-yeates-murder-charge | date = 2011-10-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。塔巴克的父母共有5个孩子，他是家中老幺<ref name="Guardian28102011" />，在[[埃因霍温|埃因霍温]]以北约34公里的[[于登|于登]]（{{lang|en|Uden}}）长大<ref name="BBC28102011">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15259135 | title = Vincent Tabak: Neighbour remembers 'introverted' child | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120107061802/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15259135 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2012-01-07 }}</ref>。案件审理工作结束后，塔巴克童年时期的邻居约翰·马索尔（{{lang|en|John Massoeurs}}）回忆称，塔巴克为人聪明，但个性内向孤僻。1996年，塔巴克进入[[埃因霍温理工大学|埃因霍温理工大学]]深造，于2003年取得建筑、建设和规划[[理学硕士|理学硕士学位]]，接下来又开始攻读[[哲学博士|哲学博士]]学位，其论文主要研究人们会如何使用办公楼和公共区域的空间，这篇论文于2008年出版。<ref name="Guardian28102011" /><ref name="BBC28102011" />

2007年完成学业后，他进入位于[[巴斯_(萨默塞特郡)|巴斯]]的[[布罗哈波尔德工程|布罗哈波尔德]]（{{lang|en|Buro Happold}}）工程咨询公司工作，然后移居英国并住当地一套公寓。他的工作职责是“人流分析”，这需要他研究人们在包括学校、机场和体育场馆在内的各种公共空间内会如何走动。塔巴克通过《[[卫报|卫报]]》的线上约会网站“灵魂伴侣”（{{lang|en|Soulmates}}）结识了一名女性并开始交往。之后有报道称，她是塔巴克第一个认真交往的女友。他还在论文中向女友致谢，其中写道：“我对她走进我的生活感到非常幸福。”2009年6月，两人搬进布里斯托尔卡宁格路的一个套间<ref name="Guardian28102011" />。乔安娜·叶茨和男友于2010年10月搬到旁边的公寓，但她和塔巴克在12月17日前并没有见过面<ref name="BBC28102011" />。

杀害叶茨后，塔巴克看到媒体的相关报道，然后企图将谋杀嫌疑引到杰弗里斯身上，自己则在荷兰同亲友共度新年。他曾致电雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警方，称杰弗里斯曾在12月17日晚开车出门，警方于是派罪案调查组探员卡伦·托马斯（{{lang|en|Karen Thomas}}）飞往[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]向他问话。两人于12月31日在[[阿姆斯特丹史基浦机场|阿姆斯特丹史基浦机场]]碰头，塔巴克详细阐述他的说法，但托马斯对之产生怀疑，因为塔巴克的证词与之前电话中存在不符，还对正在进行的法医检验工作表现出异常兴趣。<ref name="Guardian-2011-10-28" />

叶茨被杀前的几个月里，塔巴克在英国和美国出差期间曾用电脑查找过多家提供[[应召女郎|应召女郎]]的机构，还用电话联系过多个妓女<ref>{{cite news | last = Evans | first = Martin | title = Vincent Tabak 'regularly contacted prostitutes' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118215109/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8847825/Vincent-Tabak-regularly-contacted-prostitutes.html | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | newspaper = The Daily Telegraph | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8847825/Vincent-Tabak-regularly-contacted-prostitutes.html | archivedate = 2015-11-18 | date = 2011-10-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 }}</ref>。他还曾查看一些描绘女性被男性主导控制的暴力[[互联网色情片|互联网色情片]]，还有这些女性被绑起来并堵住嘴巴、亦或被掐住脖子的照片。案件调查期间，警方在塔巴克的电脑上发现神似叶茨的女性照片，其中一张显示该女性拉起上衣，露出内衣和乳房。他人发现叶茨的尸体时，她身上也穿着类似上述照片的粉红色上衣。<ref name="Guardian28102011" />

案件开审后，检方[[御用大律师|御用大律师]]奈杰尔·利克雷（{{lang|en|Nigel Lickley}}）主张让陪审团了解塔巴克所做所为的严重性：“要（这样）夺走一个女人的生命，不但需要用力掐住她（的脖子），而且还要保持足够长的时间”<ref name="Guardian28102011" />。法官认为，塔巴克观看色情片并不能说明他的行为存在[[蓄意谋杀|预谋]]，所以这方面信息不在检方的呈庭证据内<ref>{{cite news | last = Kelly | first = Chris | title = Vincent Tabak 'viewed violent web porn' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2015-08-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150818084957/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-14904647 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-14904647 }}</ref>。案件审理结束后，警方又在塔巴克的笔记本电脑上发现[[儿童色情|儿童色情]]图片<ref>{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/01/child-porn-found-vincent-tabak | title = Images of child sexual abuse found on Vincent Tabak's laptop | work = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-11-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211024816/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/01/child-porn-found-vincent-tabak | accessdate = 2015-12-07 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2013年12月，皇家检控署宣布会就持有儿童色情图片起诉塔巴克<ref>{{cite news |first=Michael |last=Ribbeck |title=Vincent Tabak, killer of Bristol landscape architect Jo Yeates, to face child porn charges |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bristol Post |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211045800/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Jo-Yeates-killer-Vincent-Tabak-face-child-porn/story-20258748-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-12-11 |date=2013-12-04 |accessdate=2015-12-07 |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Jo-Yeates-killer-Vincent-Tabak-face-child-porn/story-20258748-detail/story.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Joanna Yeates's murderer to be prosecuted for having 'indecent images of children' | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231213247/http://www.cheddarvalleygazette.co.uk/Joanna-Yeates-s-murderer-prosecuted-having/story-20266238-detail/story.html#ixzz2on3YngF8 | publisher = Local World | newspaper = Cheddar Valley Gazette | url = http://www.cheddarvalleygazette.co.uk/Joanna-Yeates-s-murderer-prosecuted-having/story-20266238-detail/story.html#ixzz2on3YngF8 | date = 2013-12-08 | archivedate = 2013-12-31 | accessdate = 2015-12-07 }}</ref>。2015年3月2日，塔巴克承认犯下拥有儿童不雅图片的罪行，被判入狱10个月<ref name="images">{{cite news | work = BBC News | publisher = BBC | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017004639/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-gloucestershire-31700109 | archivedate = 2015-10-17 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-gloucestershire-31700109 | title = Jo Yeates' killer Vincent Tabak admits possessing indecent images of children | date = 2015-03-02 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 }}</ref>。

=== 庭审 ===
2011年10月4日，文森斯·塔巴克谋杀乔安娜·叶茨案在布里斯托尔[[皇室法院|皇室法院]]开审，由法官菲爾德主持、陪审团审理<ref name="trialstarts">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-14990517 |work=BBC News |publisher=BBC |title=Trial starts of Jo Yeates murder accused Vincent Tabak |date=2011-10-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120101164725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-14990517 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archivedate=2012-01-01 }}</ref>。被告的庭审辩护律师是[[御用大律师|御用大律师]]威廉·克莱格（{{lang|en|William Clegg}}）<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111231122158/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15334969 | archivedate = 2011-12-31 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15334969 | title = Vincent Tabak trial: Yeates 'strangled for 20 seconds' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-17 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 }}</ref>，奈杰尔·利克雷则代表检方<ref name="bbc11Oct2011" />。塔巴克当庭承认犯下[[误杀|误杀]]错，但没有预谋杀人<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15402363 | title = Vincent Tabak trial: Jo Yeates killing 'not sexually motivated' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-21 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archive-date = 2021-12-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211218082214/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15402363 }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite news | first = Terri | last = Judd | title = Tabak denies sexual motive for strangling | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120825214155/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/tabak-denies-sexual-motive-for-strangling-2374261.html | publisher = Independent Print Limited | work = The Independent | date = 2011-10-22 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/tabak-denies-sexual-motive-for-strangling-2374261.html | archivedate = 2012-08-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

检方首先阐述案情，指控塔巴克于2010年12月17日晚在被害人家中把到家还只有几分钟的叶茨勒死<ref name="Guardian-2011-10-10">{{cite news | first = Steven | last = Morris | title = Vincent Tabak was 'bored' after killing Joanna Yeates, court hears | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-10-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141207232723/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/10/vincent-tabak-bored-joanna-yeates | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/10/vincent-tabak-bored-joanna-yeates | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-07 }}</ref>，并在杀人过程中使用“充足的武力”<ref name="bbc11Oct2011" />。检方指出，被告比受害人要高30厘米左右，他利用身高和体型压倒叶茨，用手腕把她强压在地板上，受害人的头部、颈部、躯干和手臂在挣扎期间一共受了43处伤<ref name="bbc11Oct2011" /><ref name="Guardian-2011-10-11">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141207231210/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/11/vincent-tabak-joanna-yeates | first = Steven | last = Morris | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/oct/11/vincent-tabak-joanna-yeates | title = Joanna Yeates 'struggled violently for her life' court hears | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-10-11 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-12-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，其中包括割伤和瘀伤，鼻子也因此骨折<ref name="Guardian-2011-10-11" />。利克雷向法庭强调，这段挣扎的持续时间很长，叶茨是在痛苦之下缓慢死去<ref name="bbc11Oct2011" />。不过，他并没有在庭上解读塔巴克攻击叶茨的动机<ref name="Telegraph-2011-10-11" />。

呈庭证据表明，塔巴克杀害叶茨后试图通过异地抛尸隐蔽罪行<ref name="Guardian-2011-10-11" />，陪审团还得知，从受害人尸体上取得的{{lang|en|DNA}}同被告相符<ref name="bbc11Oct2011" />。死者膝盖后方位置的牛仔裤上存在{{lang|en|DNA}}样品，这表明被告扛起尸体时曾抓住她的腿部，布料纤维残留则说明尸体曾接触过塔巴克的外套和汽车，办案人员还在抛尸现场附近某个可以俯瞰采石场的地方墙壁上发现血液<ref name="Guardian-2011-10-11" />。检方还称，被告曾在案件调查期间试图陷害克里斯托弗·杰弗里斯，叶茨被害后的几天里，他还在网上搜索有关尸体分解所需时间、以及克利夫顿地区垃圾收集的日期等信息<ref name="Telegraph-2011-10-11" /><ref name="Guardian-2011-10-10" />。

塔巴克辩称，他杀害叶茨并非出于性方面动机<ref name="autogenerated2" /><ref name="autogenerated1" />，他在做证时还称，自己当时只是想要亲吻受害人，但她这时大声喊叫，他只是想让她安静下来而失手将其杀害。被告还称，叶茨在他面前表现轻浮，邀请他进屋共饮，后来她开始尖叫，自己于是抓住她的手来捂住她的嘴并掐住脖子，只想让她静下来。<ref name="conviction">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15448121 | title = Vincent Tabak found guilty of Jo Yeates murder | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150305090314/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15448121 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-03-05 }}</ref>他否认控方有关打斗的指控<ref name="conviction" />，称自己只用“极小的力道”掐住受害人的脖子，保持的时间“大概是20秒钟”<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111231122158/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15334969 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15334969 | work = BBC News | title = Vincent Tabak trial: Yeates 'strangled for 20 seconds' | publisher = BBC | date = 2011-10-17 | archivedate = 2011-12-31 }}</ref>。被告还在法庭上表示，自己弃尸后一直“心慌意乱”<ref name="autogenerated1" />。

法庭于10月26日休庭，等待陪审团商议后做出裁决<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2011-12-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111223105114/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15460916 | publisher = BBC | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15460916 | title = Vincent Tabak trial: Jury warned over sympathy during deliberation | work = BBC News | date = 2011-10-26 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 }}</ref>。经过两天的商议<ref name="conviction" />，陪审团于28日以10比2的绝对多数裁决塔巴克谋杀乔安娜·叶茨罪名成立。法庭判处被告[[無期徒刑|终身监禁]]，至少20年不得[[假释|假释]]。主审法官在量刑时表示，这起杀人罪行受到“性因素”的影响。<ref name="conviction" />

== 媒体报道引发的争议 ==
部分英国媒体对案件某些方面的报道引发争议，[[独立电视新闻|独立电视新闻]]被暂时禁止参加警方新闻发布会<ref name="Journalism-20110107-reward" />，叶茨的前房东<ref name="Guardian-2011-04-21">{{cite news | first = Roy | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2011-04-21 | last = Greenslade | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade/2011/apr/21/joanna-yeates-national-newspapers | title = Six newspapers sued for libel over Joanna Yeates coverage | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151119112735/http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade/2011/apr/21/joanna-yeates-national-newspapers | publisher = Guardian Media Group | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-11-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>和总检察长都对多家报纸提出起诉<ref name="BBC-2011-05-12">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-13371918 | title = Sun and Mirror in contempt case over Jo Yeates stories | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708032359/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-13371918 | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-05-12 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

2011年1月4日，独立电视新闻在报道中批评警方处理案件调查过程失当，雅芳郡和萨默塞特郡警隊为此暂时禁止该电视台记者参加发布案情最新进展的记者招待会<ref name="Guardian-20110105-banned">{{cite news | last = Halliday | first = Josh | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/jan/05/itv-news-joanna-yeates-investigation | title = ITV News banned from Joanna Yeates press conference | newspaper = The Guardian | archivedate = 2012-02-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120229044401/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2011/jan/05/itv-news-joanna-yeates-investigation | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-01-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。该台新闻工作者[[杰兰特·文森特|杰兰特·文森特]]（{{lang|en|Geraint Vincent}}）声称，警方在案件调查上几乎毫无进展，还质疑办案人员是否遵循正常的办案程序。据曾在杀人重案组任职的某探员声称，警局没有遵循“某些常规调查程序”，如在犯罪现场寻找新证据等<ref name="Guardian-20110105-banned" />。面对禁令，独立电视新闻批评警方企图“通过审查限制我们能够播出的信息”，警局对此向[[英国通信办公室|英国通信办公室]]投诉，称该台的报道“不公平、幼稚且不负责任”<ref name="Journalism-20110105-censorship">{{cite news | last = McAthy | first = Rachel | title = ITN accuses police of censorship over ban from Joanna Yates press conference | publisher = Mousetrap Media | work = Journalism.co.uk | url = https://www.journalism.co.uk/news/itn-accuses-police-of-censorship-over-ban-from-joanna-yeates-press-conference/s2/a542171/ | date = 2011-01-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-03-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140326033940/http://www.journalism.co.uk/news/itn-accuses-police-of-censorship-over-ban-from-joanna-yeates-press-conference/s2/a542171/ }}</ref>。警方随后取消针对电视台的禁令，但又称“将来还是会毫不犹豫地采取类似措施”<ref name="Journalism-20110107-reward" />。检方还曾考虑起诉某{{lang|en|[[Twitter|Twitter]]}}账号用户，该账号在推文中透露塔巴克曾观看带有[[窒息式性爱|窒息式性爱]]和[[绑缚_(BDSM)|奴役]]内容的互联网色情片<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213180137/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15534053 |archivedate=2011-12-13 |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15534053 |title=Legal action considered over Vincent Tabak porn tweet |publisher=BBC |work=BBC News |date=2011-11-01 |accessdate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>，但在相关推文删除后决定不再追究<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15857066 | title = Contempt charges dropped over Tabak porn tweet | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-11-23 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111125172915/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15857066 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-11-25 }}</ref>。

2011年1月5日，媒体评论员[[罗伊·格林斯莱德|罗伊·格林斯莱德]]（{{lang|en|Roy Greenslade}}）在伦敦《[[标准晚报|标准晚报]]》（{{lang|en|''Evening Standard''}}）发文，对多份报纸在叶茨的房东杰弗里斯被捕后发表-{}-针对他的负面报道表示担忧，称这些报道对于个人名声来说仿佛大规模暗杀<ref name=Standard-2011-01-05>{{cite news | first = Roy | last = Greenslade | title = Joanna Yeates case demonstrates 'casual cruelty' of journalism | publisher = Evening Standard Ltd | newspaper = Evening Standard | location = London | date = 2011-01-05 | accessdate = 2011-08-18 | archivedate = 2011-08-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110818181525/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/markets/article-23911023-joanna-yeates-case-demonstrates-casual-cruelty-of-journalism.do | url = http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/markets/article-23911023-joanna-yeates-case-demonstrates-casual-cruelty-of-journalism.do }}</ref>。他举出媒体发表的多篇报道标题及正文为例，例如《太阳报》就在标题中称曾在[[克利夫顿学院|克利夫顿学院]]任職教師的杰弗里斯古怪、花哨、猥亵而且令人毛骨悚然；《[[每日快报|每日快报]]》则在报道中引述某个曾在杰弗里斯任教期间就读克利夫顿学院、但不愿透露姓名的学生的话，称他仿佛肥佬教授般行为古怪，令学员感到害怕；《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的文章中称，克利夫顿学院的学生觉得他是“黑暗和暴力[[前卫|前卫]]电影的影迷”<ref name="Standard-2011-01-05" />。4月21日，杰弗里斯以诽谤罪名起诉《太阳报》、《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》、《[[每日星报|每日星报]]》、《每日快报》、《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》和《[[每日纪事报|每日纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''Daily Record''}}）共6家报社<ref name="Guardian-2011-04-21" />。

西蒙斯、缪尔黑德和伯顿律师事务所（{{lang|en|Simons Muirhead and Burton}}）的路易斯·查拉兰博斯（{{lang|en|Louis Charalambous}}）是杰弗里斯起诉报社的律师，2008年[[馬德琳·麥卡恩失蹤事件|馬德琳·麥卡恩失蹤事件]]调查期间，罗伯特·穆拉特（{{lang|en|Robert Murat}}）成为嫌疑人后也曾遭遇类似的指控并因此起诉媒体，然后就是在查拉兰博斯的帮助下打赢官司<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-13161170 | work = BBC News | title = Jo Yeates' landlord Christopher Jefferies to sue papers | publisher = BBC | date = 2011-04-21 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150903233315/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-13161170 | archivedate = 2015-09-03 }}</ref>。7月29日，杰弗里斯接受《太阳报》、《每日镜报》、《[[周日镜报|周日镜报]]》（{{lang|en|''Sunday Mirror''}}）、《每日纪事报》、《每日邮报》、《每日快报》、《每日星报》和《[[苏格兰人报|苏格兰人报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Scotsman''}}）在报道他被捕时的“实质性”诽谤伤害赔偿<ref name="halliday">{{cite news | last = Halliday | first = Josh | title = Sun and Mirror fined for contempt of court in Christopher Jefferies articles | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | newspaper = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823001312/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/jul/29/sun-daily-mirror-guilty-contempt | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/jul/29/sun-daily-mirror-guilty-contempt | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-07-29 | archivedate = 2015-08-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Roy | last = Greenslade | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade/2011/jul/29/joanna-yeates-national-newspapers | title = Eight newspapers pay libel damages to Christopher Jefferies | publisher = Guardian Media Group | work = The Guardian | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823001302/http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade/2011/jul/29/joanna-yeates-national-newspapers | date = 2011-07-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-08-23 }}</ref>。杰弗里斯在塔巴克定罪后接受采访，称这场风波几乎浪费了他整整一年的时间，所有计划在此期间做的事都不得不搁置。他还批评政府更改[[法律援助|法律援助]]方面法律的计划，因为人们采用法律手段同报纸对抗的途径本来就很少，再在法律援助上增加更多条条框框，只会令事态雪上加霜。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-bristol-15551619 | title = Jo Yeates' landlord Christopher Jefferies 'getting on with life' | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151203105247/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-15551619 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-12-03 }}</ref>

2010年12月31日，[[英格兰和威尔士总检察长|英格兰和威尔士总检察长]][[多米尼克·格里夫|多米尼克·格里夫]]（{{lang|en|Dominic Grieve}}）表示，他正考虑根据《[[藐视法庭|1981年藐视法庭法令]]》强制要求媒体不得发布有可能损及未来庭审公正性的信息<ref name="BBC-20101231-concerns" />。[[犯罪学|犯罪学]]教授[[大衛·威爾遜_(犯罪學教授)|大卫·威尔逊]]（{{lang|en|David Wilson}}）针对英国全国范围媒体对这起谋杀案的高度关注评论：“英国公众喜欢侦探剧……这是种非常英国化的现象。我们是第一个用谋杀案来卖报纸的国家，这种文化比其他地方更加根深蒂固<ref name="Guardian-20101231-captured">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/31/joanna-yeates-murder-bristol | title = Joanna Yeates: How fate of 'ideal victim' captured nation's attention | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141104234719/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/dec/31/joanna-yeates-murder-bristol | date = 2010-12-31 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-11-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。”在威尔逊看来，叶茨身为[[失踪白种女性综合症|白种女性专业人士]]，对于媒体来说可谓是“理想的受害者”<ref name="Guardian-20101231-captured" />。1月1日，叶茨的男友里尔登针对杰弗里斯被捕后的新闻报道称：“乔的生命就这样悲剧性地中断了，但社会和新闻媒体对于现在还清白无辜的人却这样横加指责，对其人格大放冷箭，这种行径是可耻的<ref name="BBC-20100101">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12103421 | title = Jo Yeates: Family statements in full | publisher = BBC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520140928/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12103421 | work = BBC News | date = 2011-01-01 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。”

2011年5月12日，行政法院批准总检查长以藐视法庭罪起诉《太阳报》和《每日镜报》，指控两家报纸在报道杰弗里斯被捕的消息时有逾矩行为<ref name="BBC-2011-05-12" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Sun and Mirror accused of Jo Yeates contempt | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-07-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425075212/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14024079 | archivedate = 2012-04-25 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-14024079 }}</ref>。7月29日，主審案件的[[英格兰及威尔斯首席法官|首席法官]][[賈奇男爵伊格爾·賈奇|賈奇勳爵]]、[[英格蘭及威爾斯上訴法院|上訴法院]]法官[[金紀德的托馬斯男爵約翰·托馬斯|約翰·托馬斯爵士]]和[[英格蘭及威爾斯高等法院|高等法院]]法官[[羅伯特·歐文_(法官)|羅伯特·歐文爵士]]裁定两家报纸藐视法庭罪名成立，《太阳报》被处罚金1.8万英镑，《每日镜报》5万英镑<ref name="halliday" />。其中賈奇勳爵在判詞中表示：“在我们看来，这是原则问题，对被捕犯罪嫌疑人的中伤就是潜在的妨碍司法公正<ref>{{cite news | first = P. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112065353/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/tabloids-broke-contempt-law-over-joanna-landlord-6427657.html | deadurl = no | title = Tabloids broke contempt law over Joanna landlord | newspaper = Evening Standard | publisher = Evening Standard Ltd | date = 2011-07-29 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | last = Cheston | archivedate = 2014-01-12 | url = http://www.standard.co.uk/news/tabloids-broke-contempt-law-over-joanna-landlord-6427657.html }}</ref>。”两家报纸的出版商随后就罚款金额提出上诉，但[[英格兰和威尔斯的法院|英格兰和威尔士最高法院]]于2012年3月9日驳回《每日镜报》的上诉，《太阳报》则主动撤回上诉<ref>{{cite news | first = Josh | last = Halliday | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2012/mar/09/daily-mirror-refused-contempt-appeal?newsfeed=true | title = Daily Mirror publisher refused appeal against contempt of court fine | publisher = Guardian Media Group | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112003954/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2012/mar/09/daily-mirror-refused-contempt-appeal?newsfeed=true | work = The Guardian | date = 2012-03-09 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-01-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Mirror refused permission to appeal contempt ruling | publisher = Mousetrap Media | work = Journalism.co.uk | date = 2012-03-09 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-01-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140111215624/http://www.journalism.co.uk/news/mirror-refused-appeal-contempt-of-court-chris-jefferies/s2/a548266/ | deadurl = no | url = https://www.journalism.co.uk/news/mirror-refused-appeal-contempt-of-court-chris-jefferies/s2/a548266/ }}</ref>。

=== 后果 ===
2011年1月底，英国议会在对一项[[私人條例草案|私人條例草案]]展开辩论时一度援引叶茨案，这项法案建议对在新闻报道中透露未经起诉嫌犯姓名的记者处以6个月有期徒刑<ref>{{cite news |title=MP calls for change in the law after 'intrusive' coverage of Joanna Yeates case |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2011-01-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402130148/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/MP-calls-change-law-intrusive-coverage-Joanna-Yeates-case/story-11314354-detail/story.html |archivedate=2015-04-02 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-12-08 |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/MP-calls-change-law-intrusive-coverage-Joanna-Yeates-case/story-11314354-detail/story.html }}</ref>。法案于2010年6月由[[布罗克斯托_(英国国会选区)|布罗克斯托]][[保守党_(英国)|保守党]]议员[[安娜·索布里|安娜·索布里]]在[[英国下议院|下议院]]提出，她过去也当过记者和刑法大律师<ref name="pmb">{{cite web |url=http://services.parliament.uk/bills/2010-11/anonymityarrestedpersons.html |title=Anonymity (Arrested Persons) Bill 2010–11 |publisher=Parliament.uk |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archivedate=2015-04-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402153429/http://services.parliament.uk/bills/2010-11/anonymityarrestedpersons.html }}</ref>。2011年2月4日，索布里在下议院辩论时称：“我们在布里斯托尔看到的实际上是捕食前的狂躁和中伤。大部分报道内容不但（与案情）完全不相干，而且还有[[同性恋恐惧症|恐同]]情绪，我对此深恶痛绝。对这个人的诬蔑已经无法无天了。”<ref name="mik">{{cite web | work = Hansard: c1160 | publisher = Parliament.uk | title = Anonymity (Arrested Persons) Bill:House of Commons debates | date = 2011-02-04 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402142839/http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmhansrd/cm110204/debtext/110204-0001.htm#11020449000601 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmhansrd/cm110204/debtext/110204-0001.htm#11020449000601 }}</ref>不过，由于法案接下来受到[[2010年后的英国联合政府|保守党领导的联合政府]]反对，她主动撤回了法案<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmhansrd/cm110204/debtext/110204-0002.htm#11020449000732 | title = Anonymity (Arrested Persons) Bill – Second Reading | publisher = Parliament.uk | work = Hansard: c1215 | date = 2011-02-04 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archive-date = 2022-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220102115223/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmhansrd/cm110204/debtext/110204-0002.htm#11020449000732 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Anna Soubry calls for the anonymity of anyone arrested for a crime to be protected Tory MPs | work = ConservativeHome | publisher = The Conservative Party | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130311152852/http://conservativehome.blogs.com/parliament/2011/02/anna-soubry-calls-for-the-anonymity-of-anyone-arrested-for-a-crime-to-be-protected.html | date = 2011-02-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | url = http://s477308942.websitehome.co.uk//parliament/2011/02/anna-soubry-calls-for-the-anonymity-of-anyone-arrested-for-a-crime-to-be-protected.html | archivedate = 2013-03-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

《[[世界新闻报|世界新闻报]]》的[[世界新闻报电话窃听丑闻|窃听丑闻]]爆发后，[[英国首相|英国首相]][[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]設立[[萊韋森調查委員會|萊韋森調查委員會]]，调查英国媒体的职业素养和操守，杰弗里斯向该調查委員會作供<ref name="BBCLeveson-2011-11-28">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-15914969 | title = Leveson Inquiry: Media vilified me, Christopher Jefferies says | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150416040516/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-15914969 | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-11-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2015-04-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，称经警方问话后，媒体记者已经把他“逼上绝路”<ref>{{cite news | title = Leveson Inquiry: media witch hunt made me feel I was under house arrest, Christopher Jeffries (''sic'') | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | work = The Daily Telegraph | deadurl = no | date = 2011-11-28 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-05-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140513152839/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/leveson-inquiry/8920155/Leveson-Inquiry-media-witch-hunt-made-me-feel-I-was-under-house-arrest-Christopher-Jeffries.html | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/leveson-inquiry/8920155/Leveson-Inquiry-media-witch-hunt-made-me-feel-I-was-under-house-arrest-Christopher-Jeffries.html }}</ref>，他说：“很显然，这些小报记者已经认定是我犯下谋杀叶茨小姐的罪行，而且看起来他们也吃了秤砣铁了心要说服公众我是有罪的。他们刊出一系列针对我个人且非常严重的指控，但都是不真实的，他们以此为手段，走上抹黑我的狂热道路<ref name="BBCLeveson-2011-11-28" />。”2012年1月16日，《每日镜报》主编理查德·华莱士（{{lang|en|Richard Wallace}}）在接受调查组质询时坦承，该报对杰弗里斯被捕的报道是他担任主编职业生涯中的“黑点”<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120126092843/http://www.pressgazette.co.uk/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=48566&c=1 | url = http://www.pressgazette.co.uk/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=48566&c=1 | title = Wallace: Jefferies coverage is 'black mark on my record' | publisher = Progressive Media Group | newspaper = Press Gazette | date = 2012-01-16 | accessdate = 2012-01-26 | archivedate = 2012-01-26 }}</ref>。

