2011年1月2日，助理教区牧师丹·克拉克（{{lang|en|Dan Clark}}）在克利夫顿基督教堂主持叶茨的追悼会<ref name="Guardian-2011-01-02" />。2011年12月17日是叶茨逝世1周年，许多人来到这所教堂为她祈祷，向她的家人致以慰问和敬意<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-16219178 | title = Jo Yeates murder: Prayers on first anniversary of death | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2011-12-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120108091415/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-16219178 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2012-01-08 }}</ref>。格雷格·里尔登为纪念叶茨创立慈善网站，主要为失踪人士的家人筹集资金<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325173152/http://news.sky.com/story/827021/joanna-yeates-family-statement-in-full | url = http://news.sky.com/story/827021/joanna-yeates-family-statement-in-full | title = Joanna Yeates: Family Statement In Full | publisher = British Sky Broadcasting Limited | work = Sky News Online | date = 2011-01-01 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-03-25 }}</ref>。叶茨的亲朋好友在位于罗姆西的[[哈罗德·希利尔爵士园林|哈罗德·希利尔爵士园林]]为她栽植出一片纪念花园，叶茨求学期间曾在此工作<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-hampshire-18495846 | title = Jo Yeates Romsey butterfly meadow officially opened | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2012-06-18 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120814094601/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-hampshire-18495846 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-08-14 }}</ref>。叶茨生前工作的建筑设计合作公司和当地的[[國民保健署信託基金|國民保健署信託基金]]宣布，他们计划在叶茨生前为布里斯托尔[[南米德|南米德]]（{{lang|en|Southmead}}）一家造价4.3亿英镑新医院设计的花园内为她建立纪念碑<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Family-moved-idea-hospital-memorial/story-11302667-detail/story.html |title=Joanna Yeates' family moved by idea for Southmead Hospital memorial |publisher=Northcliffe Newspapers Group |newspaper=Bristol Evening Post |date=2011-01-20 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archivedate=2014-03-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324201310/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Family-moved-idea-hospital-memorial/story-11302667-detail/story.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

建筑设计合作公司驻布里斯托尔事务所还计划为叶茨建造纪念花园，格罗斯特郡大学则把叶茨的作品集结成书出版，还以叶茨为该校面向学员颁发的年度景观设计奖命名。建筑设计合作公司宣布会在公司成立50周年庆时举办慈善自行车赛，所筹善款将送交叶茨家人指定的慈善组织。<ref name="BristolPost-20110203-memorial">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120921072745/http://www.thisisbristol.co.uk/Colleagues-planning-memorial-murdered-Bristol-woman-Joanna-Yeates/story-11313063-detail/story.html | newspaper = Bristol Evening Post | archivedate = 2012-09-21 | url = http://www.thisisbristol.co.uk/Colleagues-planning-memorial-murdered-Bristol-woman-Joanna-Yeates/story-11313063-detail/story.html | title = Colleagues planning memorial to murdered Bristol woman Joanna Yeates | publisher = Northcliffe Newspapers Group | date = 2011-02-03 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>叶茨留下的一套地产价值4.7万英镑，其中还包括她留出来计划和里尔登一起买房的钱，由于她没有立下[[遗嘱|遗嘱]]，这些遗产均由她父母继承<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Architect-leaves-163-47-000-estate/story-11332465-detail/story.html |title=Joanna Yeates leaves ￡47,000 in estate |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bath Chronicle |date=2011-02-28 |accessdate=2014-09-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140905141809/http://www.bathchronicle.co.uk/Architect-leaves-163-47-000-estate/story-11332465-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-09-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2011年1月31日，警方将受害人的遗体送还给她的家人<ref name="SkyNews-20110131-released" />，葬礼在汉普郡安普菲尔德（{{lang|en|Ampfield}}）的圣马可教堂举行，并于2月11日下葬在教堂墓地<ref name="Guardian-20110204">{{cite news | last = Morris | first = Steven | title = Joanna Yeates funeral to take place next Friday | url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/feb/04/joanna-yeates-funeral | newspaper = The Guardian | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 2011-02-04 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-03-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324202645/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/feb/04/joanna-yeates-funeral }}</ref>，葬礼由教区牧师彼得·吉尔克斯（{{lang|en|Peter Gilks}}）主持，有约300人出席<ref name="Guardian-2011-02-22" />。

2013年，[[独立电视台|独立电视台]]订购了一部以杰弗里斯被捕为题材的剧情类电视剧<ref name="BBC-2013-11-05" />，剧集分为两集，于11月开拍，由[[杰森·沃特金斯|杰森·沃特金斯]]（{{lang|en|Jason Watkins}}）饰演男主角<ref name="BBC-2013-11-05">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24810200 | title = Joanna Yeates' landlord focus of new ITV drama | publisher = BBC | work = BBC News | date = 2013-11-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archivedate = 2014-12-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141211115818/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24810200 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。据《[[布里斯托尔邮报|布里斯托尔邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''Bristol Post''}}）报道，该节目剧本得到杰弗里斯本人首肯，他也支持这个项目<ref>{{cite news |title=Filming continues in Clifton, Bristol, on Christopher Jefferies TV drama |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bristol Post |date=2013-11-15 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archivedate=2014-12-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211034243/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Filmiing-continues-Clifton-Bristol-Christopher/story-20085771-detail/story.html |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Filmiing-continues-Clifton-Bristol-Christopher/story-20085771-detail/story.html }}</ref>。剧集定名《师道尊严》（{{lang|en|''The Lost Honour of Christopher Jefferies''}}），于2014年12月10至11日播映<ref>{{cite news | first = Stephen | last = Moss | script-title = en:Peter Morgan: when I saw Christopher Jefferies I thought they’d got their man | publisher = Guardian Media Group | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2014-12-07 | accessdate = 2015-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151031101417/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/dec/07/-sp-peter-morgan-christopher-jefferies-tv-drama-joanna-yeates | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/dec/07/-sp-peter-morgan-christopher-jefferies-tv-drama-joanna-yeates }}</ref>。2015年5月，该剧在[[2015年英国学术电视奖|2015年]][[英国学术电视奖|英国学术电视奖]]角逐中获最佳迷你剧和最佳男主角奖<ref>{{cite news |title=The Lost Honour of Christopher Jefferies scoops two BAFTAs |publisher=Local World |newspaper=Bristol Post |date=2015-05-10 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archivedate=2015-07-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719050846/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Lost-Honour-Christopher-Jefferies-scoops-BAFTAs/story-26475472-detail/story.html |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Lost-Honour-Christopher-Jefferies-scoops-BAFTAs/story-26475472-detail/story.html }}</ref>。2015年3月26日，[[英国第五台|英国第五台]]纪录片节目《谋杀倒计时》（{{lang|en|''Countdown to Murder''}}）播出以叶茨案为题材的节目，题为《杀手隔壁：乔安娜·叶茨的最后时刻》（{{lang|en|''The Killer Next Door: The Last Hours of Joanna Yeates''}}）<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815022837/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Documentary-Joanna-Yeates-murderer-Vincent-Tabak/story-26237304-detail/story.html |newspaper=Bristol Post |date=2015-03-26 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/Documentary-Joanna-Yeates-murderer-Vincent-Tabak/story-26237304-detail/story.html |title=Documentary about Joanna Yeates and murderer Vincent Tabak airs tonight |publisher=Local World |archivedate=2015-08-15 }}</ref>。
